title: Texas Won't Stop Denying Immigrants' Children Birth Certificates -- For Now
text: Texas officials do not have to make it easier for undocumented immigrants to get birth certificates for their children born in the state while a legal challenge proceeds in court, a federal judge ruled. U.S. District Judge Robert Pitman
